                        <pf>Dr.</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Dr. Harper resigned as pastor of the Presbyterian Church of Shippensburg.
                    He had served the congregation for almost thirty years. His flock granted him an
                    annuity of $500 in expression of their appreciation.</summary>
                <note/>
